{"title":"Vivian Maier: Unseen Work","link":"https://kottke.org/24/08/vivian-maier-unseen-work","date":1724174020000,"content":"\n        <p><a href=\"https://newyork.fotografiska.com/en/exhibitions/vivian-maier\">The first major US retrospective of Vivian Maier’s photography</a> is currently on display at Fotografiska New York through Sept 29. Maier was a street photographer whose work was <a href=\"https://kottke.org/09/10/vivian-maier-recently-discovered-street-photographer\">discovered in 2007</a> and is now recognized “alongside the greatest masters of the twentieth century”.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-01.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-01.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1300\" alt=\"black &amp; white photo of a woman looking to the right in front of a building\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-02.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-02.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1300\" alt=\"black &amp; white photo of two girls playing on the street in front of a car\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-03.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-03.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-03.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1300\" alt=\"black &amp; white self portrait of Vivian Maier reflected in a store window\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-04.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-04.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-04.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"2554\" alt=\"two black &amp; white photos of a man and a child sittng on a bench with a balloon\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-05.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-05.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vivian-maier-24-05.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"886\" alt=\"photo of three people on a street corner, all wearing the color yellow\" /></p>\n\n<p>You can see much more of Maier’s work on <a href=\"https://www.vivianmaier.com/\">this website of her work</a>.</p>\n\n        \n\n         <p><strong>Tags:</strong> <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/museums\">museums</a> · <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/photography\">photography</a> · <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/Vivian%20Maier\">Vivian Maier</a></p>\n\n         <p>💬 <a href=\"https://kottke.org/24/08/vivian-maier-unseen-work\">Join the discussion on kottke.org</a> →</p>\n\n    ","author":"Jason Kottke","siteTitle":"Kottke","siteHash":"89a883271b4598f9b33ebe87be70d38557bcd266e68aee521a8f93622e0ab723","entryHash":"d2b13a3fe3e47307e3c0a3b64e98a48cbe74172304268687f293a19335308875","category":"Sites"}